\newlabel{fig:stability}{{6}{1}{Numerical stability heatmap: each cell shows \(\log _{10} |f(x) - f(x^*)|\) for a (starting point, step size) combination, with 48 total evaluations. The right panel reports the aggregate stability score of 1.00 from \protect \texttt {check\_numerical\_stability()}}{fig:stability}{}}
